  "title": "CARPENTER SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Schedules, assigns and plans the work of carpentry factory personnel performing a variety of carpentry projects.</li><li>Plans and develops work schedules, equipment usage schedules, priority of carpentry expenditures and procedures for equipment maintenance.</li><li>Supervises carpenters to ensure safety and quality in the performance of assigned tasks.</li><li>Take measurements and calculate the size and amount of material needed.</li><li>Constructs custom cabinetry and furniture as needed; repairs or modifies furniture as needed.</li><li>Conform to an established work schedule.</li><li>Reading blueprints, drawings and sketches to fully grasp requirements.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Good interpersonal communication and problem solving skills</li><li>Good management of materials cost and stock inventory</li><li>Joinery and cabinet making skills</li><li>Able to work for long hours period or night shift</li><li>Able to work on weekends and public holiday<a href=\"https://sg.indeed.com/career-advice\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><a href=\"https://sg.indeed.com/browsejobs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><a href=\"https://sg.indeed.com/companies/browse-companies\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><a href=\"https://sg.indeed.com/career/salaries\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><a href=\"https://www.indeedevents.com/en-sg/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><a href=\"https://sg.indeed.com/worldwide\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><a href=\"https://sg.indeed.com/about\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></li></ul>",
